graph TD
    %% Phase 1: Group Creation
    subgraph Phase1 [Phase 1: Group Creation - Semi-Automated]
        A[Google Sheet: 2000 Rows] -->|Ingest| B[(Portal DB)]
        B --> C{Portal sends WA to Admin}
        C -->|Request| D[Admin creates group & sends link]
        D -->|Reply| E[Portal captures & stores link]
        E --> F[Status: 487/2000 Created]
    end

    %% Phase 2: User Invitations
    subgraph Phase2 [Phase 2: User Invitations - Automated]
        F --> G[For each group with link]
        G --> H[Portal sends WA to assigned Users]
        H --> I[Invite Sent Status]
    end

    %% Phase 3: Tracking
    subgraph Phase3 [Phase 3: Tracking & Reminders]
        I --> J{Tracking Strategy}
        
        J -->|Option A| K[Ask Admin for member count]
        J -->|Option B| L[Ask Users: Have you joined?]
        J -->|Option C| M[Admin uploads screenshot/list]
        
        K & L & M --> N[Portal parses & reconciles DB]
    end

